<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#bd0f5b14e0bba8bb7ec7e8a64b26e035>.
<#bd0f5b14e0bba8bb7ec7e8a64b26e035> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d8ec2980-752c-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3>;
