}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b802a57db8acffd13d067ead7123915f>.
<#b802a57db8acffd13d067ead7123915f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.naturvardsverket.se/resources/d0430cec-4b3d-4b4d-ac21-5b2e540c8c6c>;
